        	function submitAndAppendForm(formId, tableObject){
        		formElement = $(formId);
        		actionUrl = formElement.action;
        		originalUrl = actionUrl;
        		var objects = tableObject.getSelectedObjects();
        
        		var ids = new Array();
        		for (var i=0; i < objects.length; i++) {
        			ids.push(objects[i].fileName);
        		}		
        
        		if( ids.length >= 1 ){
        			actionUrl += "?selectedFiles=" + ids.join("&selectedFiles=");
        			formElement.action = actionUrl;
        			formElement.submit();			
        		}
        		formElement.action = originalUrl;
        	}
        </script>

        function disableAckNotification(tableComponent){
        	if (tableComponent.getSelectedObjects ) {
        		var selectedObjects = tableComponent.getSelectedObjects();
        		for (var i=0; i < selectedObjects.length; i++) {
        			if (selectedObjects[i].acknowledgedUser != undefined) {
        				return (false);
        			}
        		}
        	    return true;
        	} else {
        		return false;
        	}
        }

        <script language="javascript">
        
        function displayObject(checkbox, obj) {
            obj = getObject(obj);
            if (obj == null) {
                return;
            }
            if(checkbox.checked)
            {
                 obj.style.display =  'block';
                 obj.style.visibility = 'visible';
            }
            else
            {
                 obj.style.display = 'none';
                 obj.style.visibility='hidden';
            }
        }
        
        function getObject(obj) {
            if (document.getElementById) {
                obj = document.getElementById(obj);
            } else if (document.all) {
                obj = document.all.item(obj);
            } else {
                obj = null;
            }
            return obj;
        }
        
        function changeValue(obj) {
        	if ( obj.id == "smtpAuthenticationRequired" ) {
        		hiddenAuthenticationRequired = getObject('hiddenSmtpAuthenticationRequired');
        	} else if ( obj.id == "directoryServerUseSSL" ) {
        		hiddenAuthenticationRequired = getObject('hiddenDirectoryServerUseSSL');
        	} else {
        		hiddenAuthenticationRequired = getObject('hiddenDirectoryServerAuthenticationRequired');
        		if ( obj.checked == false ) {
        			// If it isn't checked now - then it was checked previously - 
        			// so go figure out how many users impacted
        			var _url = "numberOfUsersAuthenticatingAgainstDirectoryServer.action";
        		    doSimpleXMLHttpRequest(_url, {})
        			    .addCallbacks(asyncNumberOfUsersCheckResponse, 
        			            function (request) {
        			                    reportError(request.responseText);
        			            }
        			    );
        		} else {
        			// it is checked now - so go ahead and remove the error label that
        			// may have been created
        			var labelDiv = getObject('wwctrl_directoryServerAuthenticationRequired');
           			var existingErrorLabel = getObject('changeAuthenticationErrorLabel');
           			if ( existingErrorLabel != null ) {
        	   			labelDiv.removeChild(existingErrorLabel);
        	   		}
           		}	
        	}	
        
        	if ( obj.checked == true ) {
        		hiddenAuthenticationRequired.value = 'true';
        	} else {
        		hiddenAuthenticationRequired.value = 'false';
        	}	
        }
        
        function checkAll(obj){
        	if(obj.checked == true ) {
        		document.getElementById("operators").checked = true;
        		document.getElementById("operatorTeams").checked = true;
        		document.getElementById("devices").checked = true;
        		document.getElementById("accessories").checked = true;
        		document.getElementById("taskPacakges").checked = true;
        	}
        	else{
        		document.getElementById("operators").checked = false;
        		document.getElementById("operatorTeams").checked = false;
        		document.getElementById("devices").checked = false;
        		document.getElementById("accessories").checked = false;
        		document.getElementById("taskPacakges").checked = false;
        	}
        }
        
        
        
        function asyncNumberOfUsersCheckResponse(request) {
        	var labelDiv = getObject('wwctrl_directoryServerAuthenticationRequired');
           	var data = evalJSONRequest(request);
           	if(data != null) {
           		var existingErrorLabel = getObject('changeAuthenticationErrorLabel');
           		var newErrorLabel = 
           			LABEL({'id':'changeAuthenticationErrorLabel',
           				   'name':'changeAuthenticationErrorLabel',
           				   'class':'listErrorMessage'}, data.value);
        		if ( existingErrorLabel == null ) {
        			// We haven't had this before - so we need to create it
           			appendChildNodes(labelDiv, newErrorLabel);
           		} else {
           			// The label exists - replace it with the new one
           			labelDiv.replaceChild(existingErrorLabel, newErrorLabel);
           		}	
           	} 
        }
        
        function testConnectionToDirectoryServer() {
        	var _url = "testConnectionToDirectoryServer.action";
            var useSSL = getObject('hiddenDirectoryServerUseSSL');
            var hostName = getObject('directoryServerHost');
            var hostPort = getObject('directoryServerPort');
            var searchUser = getObject('directoryServerSearchUserName');
            var searchPass = getObject('directoryServerSearchPassword');
            var searchBase = getObject('directoryServerSearchBase');
            var searchAttr = getObject('directoryServerSearchableAttribute');
            var testUser = getObject('directoryServerTestUser');	
        	var params = "directoryServerUseSSL=" + useSSL.value +
        	                            "&directoryServerHost=" + hostName.value + 
        	                            "&directoryServerPort=" + hostPort.value +  
                                        "&directoryServerSearchUserName=" + searchUser.value+ 
                                        "&directoryServerSearchPassword=" + searchPass.value + 
                                        "&directoryServerSearchBase=" + searchBase.value + 
                                        "&directoryServerSearchableAttribute=" + searchAttr.value + 
                                        "&directoryServerTestUser=" + testUser.value + 
                                        "&"+getCsrfTokenUrlParameter();
            var  req, reqResult = "";  
        	req = getXMLHttpRequest();
            req.open("POST", _url, true);	
            req.setRequestHeader("Content-type", "application/x-www-form-urlencoded");
            reqResult = sendXMLHttpRequest(req, params);
        	reqResult.addCallbacks(asyncReturnOfTestConnectionToDirectoryServer, 
        	            function (request) {
        	                    reportError(request.responseText);
        	            }
        	    );
        }
        
        function asyncReturnOfTestConnectionToDirectoryServer(request) {
           	var data = evalJSONRequest(request);
           	if(data != null) {
           		var testAreaDiv = getObject('testArea');
        		var label=getObject('testResults');   		
        		var newErrorLabel = null;
           		
        		if (data.connected=='true') {
        	   		newErrorLabel = 
           				LABEL({'id':'testResults',
           			   	 	  'name':'testResults',
           			   	 	  'class':'listSuccessMessage'}, data.value);
           		} else {
        	   		newErrorLabel = 
           				LABEL({'id':'testResults',
           			   	 	  'name':'testResults',
           			   	 	  'class':'listErrorMessage'}, data.value);
        		}   		
           			   	 	  
        		if (label != null) {
        	   		testAreaDiv.removeChild(label);
        	   	}
        		appendChildNodes(testAreaDiv, newErrorLabel);
        	}
        }
        
        var errorList = new Array();
        
        function displayErrors(index) {
           
           errorDiv = getObject('purgeLimitError_' + index);
           
           var archiveValue;
           var purgeValue;
           
           // this may need to be changed later, to use $ syntax   
           purgeValue = document.getElementById("purgeValue_"+index).value;
           archiveElement = document.getElementById("archiveValue_"+index);
           archiveValue = 0;
           if (archiveElement) {
        	   archiveValue = document.getElementById("archiveValue_"+index).value;
        	}
           
        
            if (purgeValue > 7 && (archiveElement && archiveValue > 0))
            {           
                 errorDiv.style.display =  'block';
                 errorDiv.style.visibility = 'visible';
                 errorList[index]=true;
                 
            }
            else
            {         
                 errorDiv.style.display = 'none';
                 errorDiv.style.visibility='hidden';
                 errorList[index]=false;
            }
        }
        
        
        function displayDayWarning(obj,purgeOrArchive,index,maxPurgeArchiveDays) {
        	warningDiv = getObject(purgeOrArchive + 'DayWarning_' + index);
        	
            var dayValue=parseInt(obj.value);
        
            if(dayValue > maxPurgeArchiveDays)
            {
                 warningDiv.style.display =  'block';
                 warningDiv.style.visibility = 'visible';
            }
            else
            {
                 warningDiv.style.display = 'none';
                 warningDiv.style.visibility='hidden';
            }
        }
        
        
        function hiddenEnable(hiddenFieldId,enabled) {
        	hiddenField = getObject(hiddenFieldId);
        
        	if ( enabled == 'true' ) {
        		hiddenField.disabled = null;
        	} else {
        		hiddenField.disabled = 'true';
        	}	
        }
        
        function undoValidationFieldPopulation(purgeOrArchive,index) {
        	hiddenField = getObject(purgeOrArchive + 'Key_' + index);
        	textbox = getObject(purgeOrArchive + 'Value_' + index);
        	
        	if ( hiddenField.disabled ) {
        		textbox.value = "";
        	}
        }

        <script type="text/javascript">
        	function submitAndAppendForm(formId, tableObject){
        		formElement = $(formId);
        		actionUrl = formElement.action;
        		originalUrl = actionUrl;
        		var objects = tableObject.getSelectedObjects();
        
        		var ids = new Array();
        		for (var i=0; i < objects.length; i++) {
        			ids.push(objects[i].fileName);
        		}		
        
        		if( ids.length >= 1 ){
        			actionUrl += "?selectedFiles=" + ids.join("&selectedFiles=");
        			formElement.action = actionUrl;
        			formElement.submit();			
        		}
        		formElement.action = originalUrl;
        	}
        </script>

            {
                 obj.style.display =  'block';
                 obj.style.visibility = 'visible';
            }
            else
            {
                 obj.style.display = 'none';
                 obj.style.visibility='hidden';
            }
        }
        
        function getObject(obj) {
            if (document.getElementById) {
                obj = document.getElementById(obj);
            } else if (document.all) {
                obj = document.all.item(obj);
            } else {
                obj = null;
            }
            return obj;
        }
        
        function changeValue(obj) {
        	if ( obj.id == "smtpAuthenticationRequired" ) {
        		hiddenAuthenticationRequired = getObject('hiddenSmtpAuthenticationRequired');
        	} else if ( obj.id == "directoryServerUseSSL" ) {
        		hiddenAuthenticationRequired = getObject('hiddenDirectoryServerUseSSL');
        	} else {
        		hiddenAuthenticationRequired = getObject('hiddenDirectoryServerAuthenticationRequired');
        		if ( obj.checked == false ) {
        			// If it isn't checked now - then it was checked previously - 
        			// so go figure out how many users impacted
        			var _url = "numberOfUsersAuthenticatingAgainstDirectoryServer.action";
        		    doSimpleXMLHttpRequest(_url, {})
        			    .addCallbacks(asyncNumberOfUsersCheckResponse, 
        			            function (request) {
        			                    reportError(request.responseText);
        			            }
        			    );
        		} else {
        			// it is checked now - so go ahead and remove the error label that
        			// may have been created
        			var labelDiv = getObject('wwctrl_directoryServerAuthenticationRequired');
           			var existingErrorLabel = getObject('changeAuthenticationErrorLabel');
           			if ( existingErrorLabel != null ) {
        	   			labelDiv.removeChild(existingErrorLabel);
        	   		}
           		}	
        	}	
        
        	if ( obj.checked == true ) {
        		hiddenAuthenticationRequired.value = 'true';
        	} else {
        		hiddenAuthenticationRequired.value = 'false';
        	}	
        }
        
        function checkAll(obj){
        	if(obj.checked == true ) {
        		document.getElementById("operators").checked = true;
        		document.getElementById("operatorTeams").checked = true;
        		document.getElementById("devices").checked = true;
        		document.getElementById("accessories").checked = true;
        		document.getElementById("taskPacakges").checked = true;
        	}
        	else{
        		document.getElementById("operators").checked = false;
        		document.getElementById("operatorTeams").checked = false;
        		document.getElementById("devices").checked = false;
        		document.getElementById("accessories").checked = false;
        		document.getElementById("taskPacakges").checked = false;
        	}
        }
        
        
        
        function asyncNumberOfUsersCheckResponse(request) {
        	var labelDiv = getObject('wwctrl_directoryServerAuthenticationRequired');
           	var data = evalJSONRequest(request);
           	if(data != null) {
           		var existingErrorLabel = getObject('changeAuthenticationErrorLabel');
           		var newErrorLabel = 
           			LABEL({'id':'changeAuthenticationErrorLabel',
           				   'name':'changeAuthenticationErrorLabel',
           				   'class':'listErrorMessage'}, data.value);
        		if ( existingErrorLabel == null ) {
        			// We haven't had this before - so we need to create it
           			appendChildNodes(labelDiv, newErrorLabel);
           		} else {
           			// The label exists - replace it with the new one
           			labelDiv.replaceChild(existingErrorLabel, newErrorLabel);
           		}	
           	} 
        }
        
        function testConnectionToDirectoryServer() {
        	var _url = "testConnectionToDirectoryServer.action";
            var useSSL = getObject('hiddenDirectoryServerUseSSL');
            var hostName = getObject('directoryServerHost');
            var hostPort = getObject('directoryServerPort');
            var searchUser = getObject('directoryServerSearchUserName');
            var searchPass = getObject('directoryServerSearchPassword');
            var searchBase = getObject('directoryServerSearchBase');
            var searchAttr = getObject('directoryServerSearchableAttribute');
            var testUser = getObject('directoryServerTestUser');	
        	var params = "directoryServerUseSSL=" + useSSL.value +
        	                            "&directoryServerHost=" + hostName.value + 
        	                            "&directoryServerPort=" + hostPort.value +  
                                        "&directoryServerSearchUserName=" + searchUser.value+ 
                                        "&directoryServerSearchPassword=" + searchPass.value + 
                                        "&directoryServerSearchBase=" + searchBase.value + 
                                        "&directoryServerSearchableAttribute=" + searchAttr.value + 
                                        "&directoryServerTestUser=" + testUser.value + 
                                        "&"+getCsrfTokenUrlParameter();
            var  req, reqResult = "";  
        	req = getXMLHttpRequest();
            req.open("POST", _url, true);	
            req.setRequestHeader("Content-type", "application/x-www-form-urlencoded");
            reqResult = sendXMLHttpRequest(req, params);
        	reqResult.addCallbacks(asyncReturnOfTestConnectionToDirectoryServer, 
        	            function (request) {
        	                    reportError(request.responseText);
        	            }
        	    );
        }
        
        function asyncReturnOfTestConnectionToDirectoryServer(request) {
           	var data = evalJSONRequest(request);
           	if(data != null) {
           		var testAreaDiv = getObject('testArea');
        		var label=getObject('testResults');   		
        		var newErrorLabel = null;
           		
        		if (data.connected=='true') {
        	   		newErrorLabel = 
           				LABEL({'id':'testResults',
           			   	 	  'name':'testResults',
           			   	 	  'class':'listSuccessMessage'}, data.value);
           		} else {
        	   		newErrorLabel = 
           				LABEL({'id':'testResults',
           			   	 	  'name':'testResults',
           			   	 	  'class':'listErrorMessage'}, data.value);
        		}   		
           			   	 	  
        		if (label != null) {
        	   		testAreaDiv.removeChild(label);
        	   	}
        		appendChildNodes(testAreaDiv, newErrorLabel);
        	}
        }
        
        var errorList = new Array();
        
        function displayErrors(index) {
           
           errorDiv = getObject('purgeLimitError_' + index);
           
           var archiveValue;
           var purgeValue;
           
           // this may need to be changed later, to use $ syntax   
           purgeValue = document.getElementById("purgeValue_"+index).value;
           archiveElement = document.getElementById("archiveValue_"+index);
           archiveValue = 0;
           if (archiveElement) {
        	   archiveValue = document.getElementById("archiveValue_"+index).value;
        	}
           
        
            if (purgeValue > 7 && (archiveElement && archiveValue > 0))
            {           
                 errorDiv.style.display =  'block';
                 errorDiv.style.visibility = 'visible';
                 errorList[index]=true;
                 
            }
            else
            {         
                 errorDiv.style.display = 'none';
                 errorDiv.style.visibility='hidden';
                 errorList[index]=false;
            }
        }
        
        
        function displayDayWarning(obj,purgeOrArchive,index,maxPurgeArchiveDays) {
        	warningDiv = getObject(purgeOrArchive + 'DayWarning_' + index);
        	
            var dayValue=parseInt(obj.value);
        
            if(dayValue > maxPurgeArchiveDays)
            {
                 warningDiv.style.display =  'block';
                 warningDiv.style.visibility = 'visible';
            }
            else
            {
                 warningDiv.style.display = 'none';
                 warningDiv.style.visibility='hidden';
            }
        }
        
        
        function hiddenEnable(hiddenFieldId,enabled) {
        	hiddenField = getObject(hiddenFieldId);
        
        	if ( enabled == 'true' ) {
        		hiddenField.disabled = null;
        	} else {
        		hiddenField.disabled = 'true';
        	}	
        }
        
        function undoValidationFieldPopulation(purgeOrArchive,index) {
        	hiddenField = getObject(purgeOrArchive + 'Key_' + index);
        	textbox = getObject(purgeOrArchive + 'Value_' + index);
        	
        	if ( hiddenField.disabled ) {
        		textbox.value = "";
        	}
        }

        function toggleViewDetailsForSessionMessage(e){   
        	if (!e) var e = window.event
        		e.cancelBubble = true;
        	if (e.stopPropagation) e.stopPropagation();    
        	
        	if( $('detailContentsDiv').style.visibility == "visible" ){		    
            	$('viewDetailsDiv').style.visibility="hidden";
            	$('detailContentsDiv').style.visibility="hidden";
            }else{	        
            	$('viewDetailsDiv').style.visibility="visible";
            	$('detailContentsDiv').style.visibility="visible";
        	}
        }

        		$('viewDetailsDiv').style.visibility="hidden";  
        		$('detailContentsDiv').style.visibility="hidden";

        function checkSubmitted(elementId) {
            var buttonIsDisabled = hasElementClass(elementId, "disabled");
            if (!buttonIsDisabled) {
                if(submitted) {
                    alertSubmitted();
                    return false;
                } else {
                    submitted = true;
                    return true;
                }
            }
        }

            function checkForErrorMessage(request) {
                var ERROR_SUCCESS = "0";
                var ERROR_FAILURE = "1";
                var ERROR_PARTIAL = "2";
                if(request.responseText.indexOf("errorCode") != -1) {
                    try {
                        var data = evalJSONRequest(request);
                    } catch(err) {
                        log(err.toString());        
                    }   
                    if( data.errorCode == ERROR_SUCCESS ){
                        writeStatusMessage(data.generalMessage, 'actionMessage');
                    } else if( data.errorCode == ERROR_FAILURE ){
                        writeStatusMessage(data.generalMessage, 'actionMessage error');
                    }
                    return false;
                } else {    
                    return true;
                }
            }

            /**
              * Handles the response and updates the page accordingly for the
              * manage operator numbers page.
              */
            function updatePage(request) {
                theReturnLock = true;
                if (theDialog != undefined) {
                    theDialog.hide();
                }
                var data = evalJSONRequest(request);
                var message = data.generalMessage;
                var errorcode = data.errorCode;
                var returnValues = data.returnMap;
                    
                if (errorcode != "error") {
                    for ( var i=0; i < operatorIds.length; i++) {
                        var operId = operatorIds[i];
                        var pin = returnValues[operId];
                        if (pin != undefined && $("input_" + operId)) {
                            $("input_" + operId).value=pin;
                        }
                    }
                }
                    
                return errorcode;                    
            }
            
            function updatePageForOperIds(request) {
                if(request != undefined) {
                    var errorcode = updatePage(request);
                    
                    if (errorcode == "success") {
                        showAssignOperIdsAsPinsCompleteDialog();
                    } else {
                        var data = evalJSONRequest(request);
                        var message = data.generalMessage;            
                        showOperIdsErrorDialog(message);
                    }            
                }
                
            }
            
            function updatePageForSystemGen(request) {
                if(request != undefined) {
                    var errorcode = updatePage(request);
                    
                    if (errorcode == "success") {
                        showGeneratePinsCompleteDialog();
                    } else {
                        var data = evalJSONRequest(request);
                        var message = data.generalMessage;            
                        showSystemGenerateErrorDialog(message);
                    }              
                }
            }

        <script type="text/javascript">
            function hasVoiceClient35OrGreater(firmwareVersion) {
                if (firmwareVersion == undefined) {
                    return false;
                }
                
                var productCode = firmwareVersion.substr(0, 3); 
                if (productCode.toUpperCase() == "VCY" || productCode.toUpperCase() == "VMI" || productCode.toUpperCase() == "VCL" ) {
                    return true;
                }
                return checkFirmwareVersion(firmwareVersion);
            }
            
            function isDeviceOff(state){
            	 if (state=='Off'){
        		    	return false;
        		    }
            	return true;
            }
                
            function checkFirmwareVersion(fullVersionString) {
                version = fullVersionString;
                var start = version.indexOf("_V");
                var firstDot = version.indexOf(".", start);
                var secondDot = version.indexOf(".", firstDot + 1);
                        
                if (start == -1 || firstDot == -1 || secondDot == -1) {
                    return false;
                }
                        
                version = version.substring(start + "_V".length, secondDot);
                var splitVersion = version.split(".");
                if (splitVersion[0] < 3 ||
                    (splitVersion[0] == 3 &&
                     splitVersion[1] < 5)) {
                    return false;
                }
                
                return true;
            }
        </script>

        	var loadCriteria = function(e) {

        			.addCallbacks(function(data) {

        			});

        	/*
        	 * Setup the configure thresholds UI.
        	 */
        	var populateCriteria = function(data) {
        		var criteria = evalJSONRequest(data);
        		var output = "";
        		var currentType = "";
        		removeElement($('loading-indicator'));
        		appendChildNodes($('criteriaInputs'), DIV({id:'dynamic'}));

        			if (currentType != criteria[i].criterionType) {
        				appendChildNodes($('dynamic'), H3({}, criteria[i].criterionTypeDisplay));
        				currentType = criteria[i].criterionType;
        			}
        	
        			appendChildNodes($('dynamic'), 
        				DIV({'class':'criterion'}, 
        					DIV({'class':'label'}, criteria[i].nameDisplay), 
        					INPUT({type:"text", name:"valuesToApply[" + i + "]", value:criteria[i].defaultValue}),
        					SPAN({}, criteria[i].measurementDisplay)
        				)
        			);
        		}
        		
        		createTable(criteria);
        	}

        <script type="text/javascript">
        	function submitAndAppendForm(formId, tableObject){
        		formElement = $(formId);
        		actionUrl = formElement.action;
        		originalUrl = actionUrl;
        		var objects = tableObject.getSelectedObjects();
        
        		var ids = new Array();
        		for (var i=0; i < objects.length; i++) {
        			ids.push(objects[i].fileName);
        		}		
        
        		if( ids.length >= 1 ){
        			actionUrl += "?selectedFiles=" + ids.join("&selectedFiles=");
        			formElement.action = actionUrl;
        			formElement.submit();			
        		}
        		formElement.action = originalUrl;
        	}
        </script>

        function disableAckNotification(tableComponent){
        	if (tableComponent.getSelectedObjects ) {
        		var selectedObjects = tableComponent.getSelectedObjects();
        		for (var i=0; i < selectedObjects.length; i++) {
        			if (selectedObjects[i].acknowledgedUser != undefined) {
        				return (false);
        			}
        		}
        	    return true;
        	} else {
        		return false;
        	}
        }

        <script language="javascript">
        
        function displayObject(checkbox, obj) {
            obj = getObject(obj);
            if (obj == null) {
                return;
            }
            if(checkbox.checked)
            {
                 obj.style.display =  'block';
                 obj.style.visibility = 'visible';
            }
            else
            {
                 obj.style.display = 'none';
                 obj.style.visibility='hidden';
            }
        }
        
        function getObject(obj) {
            if (document.getElementById) {
                obj = document.getElementById(obj);
            } else if (document.all) {
                obj = document.all.item(obj);
            } else {
                obj = null;
            }
            return obj;
        }
        
        function changeValue(obj) {
        	if ( obj.id == "smtpAuthenticationRequired" ) {
        		hiddenAuthenticationRequired = getObject('hiddenSmtpAuthenticationRequired');
        	} else if ( obj.id == "directoryServerUseSSL" ) {
        		hiddenAuthenticationRequired = getObject('hiddenDirectoryServerUseSSL');
        	} else {
        		hiddenAuthenticationRequired = getObject('hiddenDirectoryServerAuthenticationRequired');
        		if ( obj.checked == false ) {
        			// If it isn't checked now - then it was checked previously - 
        			// so go figure out how many users impacted
        			var _url = "numberOfUsersAuthenticatingAgainstDirectoryServer.action";
        		    doSimpleXMLHttpRequest(_url, {})
        			    .addCallbacks(asyncNumberOfUsersCheckResponse, 
        			            function (request) {
        			                    reportError(request.responseText);
        			            }
        			    );
        		} else {
        			// it is checked now - so go ahead and remove the error label that
        			// may have been created
        			var labelDiv = getObject('wwctrl_directoryServerAuthenticationRequired');
           			var existingErrorLabel = getObject('changeAuthenticationErrorLabel');
           			if ( existingErrorLabel != null ) {
        	   			labelDiv.removeChild(existingErrorLabel);
        	   		}
           		}	
        	}	
        
        	if ( obj.checked == true ) {
        		hiddenAuthenticationRequired.value = 'true';
        	} else {
        		hiddenAuthenticationRequired.value = 'false';
        	}	
        }
        
        function checkAll(obj){
        	if(obj.checked == true ) {
        		document.getElementById("operators").checked = true;
        		document.getElementById("operatorTeams").checked = true;
        		document.getElementById("devices").checked = true;
        		document.getElementById("accessories").checked = true;
        		document.getElementById("taskPacakges").checked = true;
        	}
        	else{
        		document.getElementById("operators").checked = false;
        		document.getElementById("operatorTeams").checked = false;
        		document.getElementById("devices").checked = false;
        		document.getElementById("accessories").checked = false;
        		document.getElementById("taskPacakges").checked = false;
        	}
        }
        
        
        
        function asyncNumberOfUsersCheckResponse(request) {
        	var labelDiv = getObject('wwctrl_directoryServerAuthenticationRequired');
           	var data = evalJSONRequest(request);
           	if(data != null) {
           		var existingErrorLabel = getObject('changeAuthenticationErrorLabel');
           		var newErrorLabel = 
           			LABEL({'id':'changeAuthenticationErrorLabel',
           				   'name':'changeAuthenticationErrorLabel',
           				   'class':'listErrorMessage'}, data.value);
        		if ( existingErrorLabel == null ) {
        			// We haven't had this before - so we need to create it
           			appendChildNodes(labelDiv, newErrorLabel);
           		} else {
           			// The label exists - replace it with the new one
           			labelDiv.replaceChild(existingErrorLabel, newErrorLabel);
           		}	
           	} 
        }
        
        function testConnectionToDirectoryServer() {
        	var _url = "testConnectionToDirectoryServer.action";
            var useSSL = getObject('hiddenDirectoryServerUseSSL');
            var hostName = getObject('directoryServerHost');
            var hostPort = getObject('directoryServerPort');
            var searchUser = getObject('directoryServerSearchUserName');
            var searchPass = getObject('directoryServerSearchPassword');
            var searchBase = getObject('directoryServerSearchBase');
            var searchAttr = getObject('directoryServerSearchableAttribute');
            var testUser = getObject('directoryServerTestUser');	
        	var params = "directoryServerUseSSL=" + useSSL.value +
        	                            "&directoryServerHost=" + hostName.value + 
        	                            "&directoryServerPort=" + hostPort.value +  
                                        "&directoryServerSearchUserName=" + searchUser.value+ 
                                        "&directoryServerSearchPassword=" + searchPass.value + 
                                        "&directoryServerSearchBase=" + searchBase.value + 
                                        "&directoryServerSearchableAttribute=" + searchAttr.value + 
                                        "&directoryServerTestUser=" + testUser.value + 
                                        "&"+getCsrfTokenUrlParameter();
            var  req, reqResult = "";  
        	req = getXMLHttpRequest();
            req.open("POST", _url, true);	
            req.setRequestHeader("Content-type", "application/x-www-form-urlencoded");
            reqResult = sendXMLHttpRequest(req, params);
        	reqResult.addCallbacks(asyncReturnOfTestConnectionToDirectoryServer, 
        	            function (request) {
        	                    reportError(request.responseText);
        	            }
        	    );
        }
        
        function asyncReturnOfTestConnectionToDirectoryServer(request) {
           	var data = evalJSONRequest(request);
           	if(data != null) {
           		var testAreaDiv = getObject('testArea');
        		var label=getObject('testResults');   		
        		var newErrorLabel = null;
           		
        		if (data.connected=='true') {
        	   		newErrorLabel = 
           				LABEL({'id':'testResults',
           			   	 	  'name':'testResults',
           			   	 	  'class':'listSuccessMessage'}, data.value);
           		} else {
        	   		newErrorLabel = 
           				LABEL({'id':'testResults',
           			   	 	  'name':'testResults',
           			   	 	  'class':'listErrorMessage'}, data.value);
        		}   		
           			   	 	  
        		if (label != null) {
        	   		testAreaDiv.removeChild(label);
        	   	}
        		appendChildNodes(testAreaDiv, newErrorLabel);
        	}
        }
        
        var errorList = new Array();
        
        function displayErrors(index) {
           
           errorDiv = getObject('purgeLimitError_' + index);
           
           var archiveValue;
           var purgeValue;
           
           // this may need to be changed later, to use $ syntax   
           purgeValue = document.getElementById("purgeValue_"+index).value;
           archiveElement = document.getElementById("archiveValue_"+index);
           archiveValue = 0;
           if (archiveElement) {
        	   archiveValue = document.getElementById("archiveValue_"+index).value;
        	}
           
        
            if (purgeValue > 7 && (archiveElement && archiveValue > 0))
            {           
                 errorDiv.style.display =  'block';
                 errorDiv.style.visibility = 'visible';
                 errorList[index]=true;
                 
            }
            else
            {         
                 errorDiv.style.display = 'none';
                 errorDiv.style.visibility='hidden';
                 errorList[index]=false;
            }
        }
        
        
        function displayDayWarning(obj,purgeOrArchive,index,maxPurgeArchiveDays) {
        	warningDiv = getObject(purgeOrArchive + 'DayWarning_' + index);
        	
            var dayValue=parseInt(obj.value);
        
            if(dayValue > maxPurgeArchiveDays)
            {
                 warningDiv.style.display =  'block';
                 warningDiv.style.visibility = 'visible';
            }
            else
            {
                 warningDiv.style.display = 'none';
                 warningDiv.style.visibility='hidden';
            }
        }
        
        
        function hiddenEnable(hiddenFieldId,enabled) {
        	hiddenField = getObject(hiddenFieldId);
        
        	if ( enabled == 'true' ) {
        		hiddenField.disabled = null;
        	} else {
        		hiddenField.disabled = 'true';
        	}	
        }
        
        function undoValidationFieldPopulation(purgeOrArchive,index) {
        	hiddenField = getObject(purgeOrArchive + 'Key_' + index);
        	textbox = getObject(purgeOrArchive + 'Value_' + index);
        	
        	if ( hiddenField.disabled ) {
        		textbox.value = "";
        	}
        }

        function toggleViewDetailsForSessionMessage(e){   
        	if (!e) var e = window.event
        		e.cancelBubble = true;
        	if (e.stopPropagation) e.stopPropagation();    
        	
        	if( $('detailContentsDiv').style.visibility == "visible" ){		    
            	$('viewDetailsDiv').style.visibility="hidden";
            	$('detailContentsDiv').style.visibility="hidden";
            }else{	        
            	$('viewDetailsDiv').style.visibility="visible";
            	$('detailContentsDiv').style.visibility="visible";
        	}
        }       
        	
        function closeViewDetailsForSessionMessage(e){   
        		$('viewDetailsDiv').style.visibility="hidden";  
        		$('detailContentsDiv').style.visibility="hidden";                 
        }
        function resetMessagesDiv() {
        	msg = $j("#messages");
        	msg.css({"left": "40%"});
        	if(msg.children("span").length > 0)
        	{
        		msg.css("visibility", "visible");
        		msg.css("display", "inline");
        	}
        }

        <script type="text/javascript">
        function checkSubmitted(elementId) {
            var buttonIsDisabled = hasElementClass(elementId, "disabled");
            if (!buttonIsDisabled) {
                if(submitted) {
                    alertSubmitted();
                    return false;
                } else {
                    submitted = true;
                    return true;
                }
            }
        }
        function alertSubmitted() {
            writeStatusMessage("Your request is being processed.", "partial");
        }
        </script>

                }
            }

        <script type="text/javascript">
        	function submitAndAppendForm(formId, tableObject){
        		formElement = $(formId);
        		actionUrl = formElement.action;
        		originalUrl = actionUrl;
        		var objects = tableObject.getSelectedObjects();
        
        		var ids = new Array();
        		for (var i=0; i < objects.length; i++) {
        			ids.push(objects[i].fileName);
        		}		
        
        		if( ids.length >= 1 ){
        			actionUrl += "?selectedFiles=" + ids.join("&selectedFiles=");
        			formElement.action = actionUrl;
        			formElement.submit();			
        		}
        		formElement.action = originalUrl;
        	}
        </script>

        				return (false);
        			}
        		}
        	    return true;
        	} else {
        		return false;
        	}
        }

        <script language="javascript">
        
        function displayObject(checkbox, obj) {
            obj = getObject(obj);
            if (obj == null) {
                return;
            }
            if(checkbox.checked)
            {
                 obj.style.display =  'block';
                 obj.style.visibility = 'visible';
            }
            else
            {
                 obj.style.display = 'none';
                 obj.style.visibility='hidden';
            }
        }
        
        function getObject(obj) {
            if (document.getElementById) {
                obj = document.getElementById(obj);
            } else if (document.all) {
                obj = document.all.item(obj);
            } else {
                obj = null;
            }
            return obj;
        }
        
        function changeValue(obj) {
        	if ( obj.id == "smtpAuthenticationRequired" ) {
        		hiddenAuthenticationRequired = getObject('hiddenSmtpAuthenticationRequired');
        	} else if ( obj.id == "directoryServerUseSSL" ) {
        		hiddenAuthenticationRequired = getObject('hiddenDirectoryServerUseSSL');
        	} else {
        		hiddenAuthenticationRequired = getObject('hiddenDirectoryServerAuthenticationRequired');
        		if ( obj.checked == false ) {
        			// If it isn't checked now - then it was checked previously - 
        			// so go figure out how many users impacted
        			var _url = "numberOfUsersAuthenticatingAgainstDirectoryServer.action";
        		    doSimpleXMLHttpRequest(_url, {})
        			    .addCallbacks(asyncNumberOfUsersCheckResponse, 
        			            function (request) {
        			                    reportError(request.responseText);
        			            }
        			    );
        		} else {
        			// it is checked now - so go ahead and remove the error label that
        			// may have been created
        			var labelDiv = getObject('wwctrl_directoryServerAuthenticationRequired');
           			var existingErrorLabel = getObject('changeAuthenticationErrorLabel');
           			if ( existingErrorLabel != null ) {
        	   			labelDiv.removeChild(existingErrorLabel);
        	   		}
           		}	
        	}	
        
        	if ( obj.checked == true ) {
        		hiddenAuthenticationRequired.value = 'true';
        	} else {
        		hiddenAuthenticationRequired.value = 'false';
        	}	
        }
        
        function checkAll(obj){
        	if(obj.checked == true ) {
        		document.getElementById("operators").checked = true;
        		document.getElementById("operatorTeams").checked = true;
        		document.getElementById("devices").checked = true;
        		document.getElementById("accessories").checked = true;
        		document.getElementById("taskPacakges").checked = true;
        	}
        	else{
        		document.getElementById("operators").checked = false;
        		document.getElementById("operatorTeams").checked = false;
        		document.getElementById("devices").checked = false;
        		document.getElementById("accessories").checked = false;
        		document.getElementById("taskPacakges").checked = false;
        	}
        }
        
        
        
        function asyncNumberOfUsersCheckResponse(request) {
        	var labelDiv = getObject('wwctrl_directoryServerAuthenticationRequired');
           	var data = evalJSONRequest(request);
           	if(data != null) {
           		var existingErrorLabel = getObject('changeAuthenticationErrorLabel');
           		var newErrorLabel = 
           			LABEL({'id':'changeAuthenticationErrorLabel',
           				   'name':'changeAuthenticationErrorLabel',
           				   'class':'listErrorMessage'}, data.value);
        		if ( existingErrorLabel == null ) {
        			// We haven't had this before - so we need to create it
           			appendChildNodes(labelDiv, newErrorLabel);
           		} else {
           			// The label exists - replace it with the new one
           			labelDiv.replaceChild(existingErrorLabel, newErrorLabel);
           		}	
           	} 
        }
        
        function testConnectionToDirectoryServer() {
        	var _url = "testConnectionToDirectoryServer.action";
            var useSSL = getObject('hiddenDirectoryServerUseSSL');
            var hostName = getObject('directoryServerHost');
            var hostPort = getObject('directoryServerPort');
            var searchUser = getObject('directoryServerSearchUserName');
            var searchPass = getObject('directoryServerSearchPassword');
            var searchBase = getObject('directoryServerSearchBase');
            var searchAttr = getObject('directoryServerSearchableAttribute');
            var testUser = getObject('directoryServerTestUser');	
        	var params = "directoryServerUseSSL=" + useSSL.value +
        	                            "&directoryServerHost=" + hostName.value + 
        	                            "&directoryServerPort=" + hostPort.value +  
                                        "&directoryServerSearchUserName=" + searchUser.value+ 
                                        "&directoryServerSearchPassword=" + searchPass.value + 
                                        "&directoryServerSearchBase=" + searchBase.value + 
                                        "&directoryServerSearchableAttribute=" + searchAttr.value + 
                                        "&directoryServerTestUser=" + testUser.value + 
                                        "&"+getCsrfTokenUrlParameter();
            var  req, reqResult = "";  
        	req = getXMLHttpRequest();
            req.open("POST", _url, true);	
            req.setRequestHeader("Content-type", "application/x-www-form-urlencoded");
            reqResult = sendXMLHttpRequest(req, params);
        	reqResult.addCallbacks(asyncReturnOfTestConnectionToDirectoryServer, 
        	            function (request) {
        	                    reportError(request.responseText);
        	            }
        	    );
        }
        
        function asyncReturnOfTestConnectionToDirectoryServer(request) {
           	var data = evalJSONRequest(request);
           	if(data != null) {
           		var testAreaDiv = getObject('testArea');
        		var label=getObject('testResults');   		
        		var newErrorLabel = null;
           		
        		if (data.connected=='true') {
        	   		newErrorLabel = 
           				LABEL({'id':'testResults',
           			   	 	  'name':'testResults',
           			   	 	  'class':'listSuccessMessage'}, data.value);
           		} else {
        	   		newErrorLabel = 
           				LABEL({'id':'testResults',
           			   	 	  'name':'testResults',
           			   	 	  'class':'listErrorMessage'}, data.value);
        		}   		
           			   	 	  
        		if (label != null) {
        	   		testAreaDiv.removeChild(label);
        	   	}
        		appendChildNodes(testAreaDiv, newErrorLabel);
        	}
        }
        
        var errorList = new Array();
        
        function displayErrors(index) {
           
           errorDiv = getObject('purgeLimitError_' + index);
           
           var archiveValue;
           var purgeValue;
           
           // this may need to be changed later, to use $ syntax   
           purgeValue = document.getElementById("purgeValue_"+index).value;
           archiveElement = document.getElementById("archiveValue_"+index);
           archiveValue = 0;
           if (archiveElement) {
        	   archiveValue = document.getElementById("archiveValue_"+index).value;
        	}
           
        
            if (purgeValue > 7 && (archiveElement && archiveValue > 0))
            {           
                 errorDiv.style.display =  'block';
                 errorDiv.style.visibility = 'visible';
                 errorList[index]=true;
                 
            }
            else
            {         
                 errorDiv.style.display = 'none';
                 errorDiv.style.visibility='hidden';
                 errorList[index]=false;
            }
        }
        
        
        function displayDayWarning(obj,purgeOrArchive,index,maxPurgeArchiveDays) {
        	warningDiv = getObject(purgeOrArchive + 'DayWarning_' + index);
        	
            var dayValue=parseInt(obj.value);
        
            if(dayValue > maxPurgeArchiveDays)
            {
                 warningDiv.style.display =  'block';
                 warningDiv.style.visibility = 'visible';
            }
            else
            {
                 warningDiv.style.display = 'none';
                 warningDiv.style.visibility='hidden';
            }
        }
        
        
        function hiddenEnable(hiddenFieldId,enabled) {
        	hiddenField = getObject(hiddenFieldId);
        
        	if ( enabled == 'true' ) {
        		hiddenField.disabled = null;
        	} else {
        		hiddenField.disabled = 'true';
        	}	
        }
        
        function undoValidationFieldPopulation(purgeOrArchive,index) {
        	hiddenField = getObject(purgeOrArchive + 'Key_' + index);
        	textbox = getObject(purgeOrArchive + 'Value_' + index);
        	
        	if ( hiddenField.disabled ) {
        		textbox.value = "";
        	}
        }

        function toggleViewDetailsForSessionMessage(e){   
        	if (!e) var e = window.event
        		e.cancelBubble = true;
        	if (e.stopPropagation) e.stopPropagation();    
        	
        	if( $('detailContentsDiv').style.visibility == "visible" ){		    
            	$('viewDetailsDiv').style.visibility="hidden";
            	$('detailContentsDiv').style.visibility="hidden";
            }else{	        
            	$('viewDetailsDiv').style.visibility="visible";
            	$('detailContentsDiv').style.visibility="visible";
        	}
        }

        		$('viewDetailsDiv').style.visibility="hidden";  
        		$('detailContentsDiv').style.visibility="hidden";                 
        }

        function checkSubmitted(elementId) {
            var buttonIsDisabled = hasElementClass(elementId, "disabled");
            if (!buttonIsDisabled) {
                if(submitted) {
                    alertSubmitted();
                    return false;
                } else {
                    submitted = true;
                    return true;
                }
            }
        }
        function alertSubmitted() {
            writeStatusMessage("Your request is being processed.", "partial");
        }

            function checkForErrorMessage(request) {
                var ERROR_SUCCESS = "0";
                var ERROR_FAILURE = "1";
                var ERROR_PARTIAL = "2";
                if(request.responseText.indexOf("errorCode") != -1) {
                    try {
                        var data = evalJSONRequest(request);
                    } catch(err) {
                        log(err.toString());        
                    }   
                    if( data.errorCode == ERROR_SUCCESS ){
                        writeStatusMessage(data.generalMessage, 'actionMessage');
                    } else if( data.errorCode == ERROR_FAILURE ){
                        writeStatusMessage(data.generalMessage, 'actionMessage error');
                    }
                    return false;
                } else {    
                    return true;
                }
            }

            /**
              * Handles the response and updates the page accordingly for the
              * manage operator numbers page.
              */
            function updatePage(request) {
                theReturnLock = true;
                if (theDialog != undefined) {
                    theDialog.hide();
                }
                var data = evalJSONRequest(request);
                var message = data.generalMessage;
                var errorcode = data.errorCode;
                var returnValues = data.returnMap;
                    
                if (errorcode != "error") {
                    for ( var i=0; i < operatorIds.length; i++) {
                        var operId = operatorIds[i];
                        var pin = returnValues[operId];
                        if (pin != undefined && $("input_" + operId)) {
                            $("input_" + operId).value=pin;
                        }
                    }
                }
                    
                return errorcode;                    
            }
            
            function updatePageForOperIds(request) {
                if(request != undefined) {
                    var errorcode = updatePage(request);
                    
                    if (errorcode == "success") {
                        showAssignOperIdsAsPinsCompleteDialog();
                    } else {
                        var data = evalJSONRequest(request);
                        var message = data.generalMessage;            
                        showOperIdsErrorDialog(message);
                    }            
                }
                
            }
            
            function updatePageForSystemGen(request) {
                if(request != undefined) {
                    var errorcode = updatePage(request);
                    
                    if (errorcode == "success") {
                        showGeneratePinsCompleteDialog();
                    } else {
                        var data = evalJSONRequest(request);
                        var message = data.generalMessage;            
                        showSystemGenerateErrorDialog(message);
                    }              
                }
            }

        <script type="text/javascript">
            function hasVoiceClient35OrGreater(firmwareVersion) {
                if (firmwareVersion == undefined) {
                    return false;
                }
                
                var productCode = firmwareVersion.substr(0, 3); 
                if (productCode.toUpperCase() == "VCY" || productCode.toUpperCase() == "VMI" || productCode.toUpperCase() == "VCL" ) {
                    return true;
                }
                return checkFirmwareVersion(firmwareVersion);
            }
            
            function isDeviceOff(state){
            	 if (state=='Off'){
        		    	return false;
        		    }
            	return true;
            }
                
            function checkFirmwareVersion(fullVersionString) {
                version = fullVersionString;
                var start = version.indexOf("_V");
                var firstDot = version.indexOf(".", start);
                var secondDot = version.indexOf(".", firstDot + 1);
                        
                if (start == -1 || firstDot == -1 || secondDot == -1) {
                    return false;
                }
                        
                version = version.substring(start + "_V".length, secondDot);
                var splitVersion = version.split(".");
                if (splitVersion[0] < 3 ||
                    (splitVersion[0] == 3 &&
                     splitVersion[1] < 5)) {
                    return false;
                }
                
                return true;
            }
        </script>
        <script type="text/javascript">
        var criteriaUI = function(applyToSitesText, siteText) {
        	var loadCriteriaUrl = "/VoiceConsole-3wis/devices/accessory/loadCriteriaByType.action";
        	
        	/*
        	 * Retrieve the criteria from the server for the selected type.
        	 */
        	var loadCriteria = function(e) {
        		
        		var type = $('form1_batteryType').value;
        		
        		if (($('dynamic')) !== null) {
        			removeElement($('dynamic'));
        		}
        		
        		appendChildNodes($('criteriaInputs'), IMG({id:'loading-indicator', src:'/VoiceConsole-3wis/images/waiting.gif'}));
        		
        		doSimpleXMLHttpRequest(loadCriteriaUrl, { selectedBatteryType : type })
        			.addCallbacks(function(data) {
        				populateCriteria(data);
        			});
        	}
        	
        	/*
        	 * Setup the configure thresholds UI.
        	 */
        	var populateCriteria = function(data) {
        		var criteria = evalJSONRequest(data);
        		var output = "";
        		var currentType = "";
        		removeElement($('loading-indicator'));
        		appendChildNodes($('criteriaInputs'), DIV({id:'dynamic'}));
        		for (var i = 0; i < criteria.length; i++) {
        			if (currentType != criteria[i].criterionType) {
        				appendChildNodes($('dynamic'), H3({}, criteria[i].criterionTypeDisplay));
        				currentType = criteria[i].criterionType;
        			}
        	
        			appendChildNodes($('dynamic'), 
        				DIV({'class':'criterion'}, 
        					DIV({'class':'label'}, criteria[i].nameDisplay), 
        					INPUT({type:"text", name:"valuesToApply[" + i + "]", value:criteria[i].defaultValue}),
        					SPAN({}, criteria[i].measurementDisplay)
        				)
        			);
        		}
        		
        		createTable(criteria);
        	}
        	
        	/*
        	 * Create the table for selecting sites.
        	 */
        	var createTable = function(criteria) {
        		columns = TR({'class':'columnHeaderBar'},
        					TH({width:19},
        						INPUT({'class':'checkbox', type:'checkbox', value:'allSites', name:'allSites', id:'allSites'})
        					),
        					TH({}, siteText)
        		);
        		titleBar = TR({'class':'titleBar'},
        						TH({'colSpan':criteria.length+2})
        					);
        		for (var i = 0; i < criteria.length; i++) {
        			appendChildNodes(columns, TH({}, criteria[i].criterionTypeDisplay + " : " + criteria[i].nameDisplay));
        		}
        		
        		var table_head = THEAD({}, titleBar, columns);
        		var table_body = TBODY({});
        		var table = TABLE({'class':'simpleData', id:'thresholdSites'}, table_head, table_body);
        			
        		for (var s = 0; s < criteria[0].siteValues.length; s++) {
        			if (s % 2) {
        				rowClass = "even";
        			} else {
        				rowClass = "odd";
        			}
        			var siteValue = criteria[0].siteValues[s];
        			var data_row = TR({'class':rowClass},
        				TD({},
        					INPUT({'class':'checkbox', type:'checkbox', value:siteValue.siteId, name:'siteIds', id:siteValue.siteName, onclick:"javascript:uncheckSelectAll(document.thresholds.allSites, document.thresholds.siteIds);"})
        				),
        				TD({}, siteValue.siteName)
        			);
        			for (var i = 0; i < criteria.length; i++) {
        				appendChildNodes(data_row,
        					TD({}, criteria[i].siteValues[s].value)
        				);
        			}
        			appendChildNodes(table_body, data_row); 
        		}
        	
        		appendChildNodes($('dynamic'), H3({}, applyToSitesText));
        		appendChildNodes($('dynamic'), table);
        		YAHOO.util.Event.addListener('allSites', 'click', checkAllBoxHandler, [document.thresholds.allSites, document.thresholds.siteIds]);
        						 
        	}
        	
        	connect(window, 'onload', loadCriteria);
        	connect('form1_batteryType', 'onchange', loadCriteria);
        }
        </script>
